<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">

<head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=1280">
  <title>确定订单</title>
  <link href="../../../css/pages/common/common.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
  <link href="../../../css/pages/order/order-detail.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
</head>

<body>
  == Slim::Template.new('../../module/header.slim').render
  <div class="pm">
    <div class="order-createrefundtax">
      <h2>申请返还税金信息填写</h2>
      <div class="order-createrefundtax-b1">
        <div class="order-createrefundtax-b1-c1">
          <label for="alipayaccount">税单编号：</label>
          <input type="text" id="alipayaccount" />
          <a href="javascript:" class="order-createrefundtax-help">?</a>
          <span id="errorAlipayAccount" class="text-important hide">请输入正确的支付宝账户</span>
        </div>
        <div class="order-createrefundtax-b1-c1">
          <label for="alipayaccount">退税金额：</label>
          <input type="text" id="alipayaccount" />
          <span id="errorAlipayAccount" class="text-important hide">请输入正确的支付宝账户</span>
        </div>
        <div class="order-createrefundtax-b1-c1">
          <label for="alipayaccount">支付宝账户：</label>
          <input type="text" id="alipayaccount" />
          <span id="errorAlipayAccount" class="text-important hide">请输入正确的支付宝账户</span>
        </div>
        <div class="order-createrefundtax-b1-c1">
          <label for="alipayname">账户真实姓名：</label>
          <input type="text" id="alipayname" />
          <span id="errorAlipayName" class="text-important hide">请输入账户真实姓名</span>
        </div>
        <div id="img" class="order-createrefundtax-b1-c2 clearfix">
          <label class="" for="">税金缴纳证明：</label>

          <label class="comment-add-img-add" id="pickbutton">上传照片
            <input type="file" class="visuallyhidden" />
          </label>

          <p class="">返还税金需提供缴税证明，即中华人民共和国海关旅客行李、个人邮递物品进口税款缴纳证的正面照片。大小不超过5M，支持GIF,JPEG,JPG,PNG,BMP格式
          </p>
        </div>

        <input type="hidden" name="imgs1" can-value="comment.input.img0">

        <ul class="comment-add-img img-list-ul">

        </ul>
        <button class="btn btn-success btn-large btn-refer-tax">提交申请</button>
        <div id="errorNoPicTips" class="text-important hide">请上传缴税证明照片</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 弹窗 -->
  <div class="mask show"></div>
  <div class="order-createrefundtax-dialog">
    <h2>温馨提示：</h2>
    <p>样例为缴费凭证示例图，红框内是税单编号  (即除EL开头的另外一串编号)</p>
    <img src="http://img0.sfht.com/cmsres/20151216/6eb7daba-0a05-4a20-ad3f-694fb7af9341.jpeg" alt="">
    <ul>
      <li>*  请上传清晰的税金缴纳凭证，如果是邮局代缴，请将代缴手续费凭证和税金缴纳凭证一起拍照上传。</li>
      <li>*  请提供正确的税单号和税金，客服审核通过后，税金将退还至您提供的支付宝账号。</li>
    </ul>
    <a href="javascript:" class="order-createrefundtax-dialog-close">X</a>
  </div>
  <!--尾部-->
  == Slim::Template.new('../../module/footer.slim').render
  <!--尾部-->
  <script src="js/jquery-1.11.1.min.js"></script>
  <script src="js/index.js"></script>
  <script src="js/cart.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
